properties.Name: ServiceRequest
properties.Description:
A request for services made by a party.

A Service Request may be addressed immediately or require additional activity(s) or Service Request Activity(s).

Both Service Request(s) and Service Request Activity(s) involve one or more parties of various types and responsibilities and may incur costs that are charged internally or to the party.

A Service Request may be raised to an Issue if it can not be resolved or required higher visibility.

Columns.Name: ServiceRequestId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Service Request.

Columns.Name: ServiceRequestDescription
Columns.Description: A description of the service request.

Columns.Name: ServiceRequestReceivedTimestamp
Columns.Description: The timestamp that the service request was received.

Columns.Name: ServiceRequestOpenedTimestamp
Columns.Description: The timestamp that the service request was opened for processing.

Columns.Name: ServiceRequestResolutionTimestamp
Columns.Description: The timestamp that the service request was resolved or closed.

Columns.Name: TotalManhoursRequired
Columns.Description: The total number of manhours required to resolve the Service Request.

Columns.Name: TotalInternalManhours
Columns.Description: The total number of internal (organization) manhours required to resolve the Service Request.

Columns.Name: TotalExternalThirdPartyManhours
Columns.Description: The total number of external (third-party or external organization) manhours required to resolve the Service Request.

Columns.Name: TotalCustomerPartyBillableHours
Columns.Description: The total number of billable manhours associated with the Service Request.

Columns.Name: TotalChargesAmount
Columns.Description: The total charges amount charged to external parties in relationship to the Service Request.

Columns.Name: TotalInternalCostsAmount
Columns.Description: The total charges amount charged to internal parties in relationship to the Service Request.

Columns.Name: TotalChargedInternalCostsAmount
Columns.Description: The total amount of internal/activity-related costs that were chargeable.

Columns.Name: TotalChargedToCustomerAmount
Columns.Description: The total amount charged to the customer.

Columns.Name: TotalChargedToThirdPartyAmount
Columns.Description: The total amount charged to third parties.

Columns.Name: ServiceRequestTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Service Request Type.

Columns.Name: ServiceRequestPriorityId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of the Service Request Priority.

Columns.Name: PartyId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Party.

Columns.Name: OrganizationId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an organization or business unit.

Columns.Name: IssueId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of the Issue to which the Service Request is raised or related.
